<HEAD>First Family Observes Palm Sunday at Church Near White House</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   President and Mrs. Bush observed Palm Sunday by
attending a worship service at an landmark Episcopal church a block
from the White House.
   They knelt with other worshippers at the altar rail of St. John's
Episcopal Church on Lafayette Square and received Holy Communion at
